OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784830712
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to cut business rates by
OL,4,C20% for pubs, clubs and music venues
OL,6,FBusiness rates will be cut by 20% for
OL,7,Fpubs, clubs and live music venues
OL,8,Facross England from April next year,
OL,9,FDowning Street has announced.
OL,11,FThe discount will apply to nearly
OL,12,F32,000 hospitality businesses and is
OL,13,Fexpected to save a typical pub some
OL,14,F#1,100 annually, but will not be
OL,15,Favailable to the very largest live
OL,16,Fmusic venues.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
