FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784830712
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to cut business rates by
OL,4,C20% for pubs, clubs and music venues
OL,6,FThe overhaul of business rates will be
OL,7,Ffunded through a review of reliefs for
OL,8,Fbusinesses that "do not make a
OL,9,Fpositive contribution to local
OL,10,Fcommunities", such as vape shops, and
OL,11,Fa crackdown on online marketplaces
OL,12,Fthat do not comply with tax
OL,13,Fobligations, No 10 said.
OL,15,FPrime Minister Andy Burnham had
OL,16,Fpreviously pledged to raise taxes on
OL,17,Fout-of-town warehouses for online
OL,18,Fgiants like Amazon to help pay for
OL,19,Fcuts to rates for hospitality firms.
OL,26,@pD@QOUrD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784830712
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to cut business rates by
OL,4,C20% for pubs, clubs and music venues
OL,6,F"This government will back the
OL,7,Fbusinesses that people want to see in
OL,8,Ftheir communities," Burnham said.
OL,10,F"I said I would protect pubs and local
OL,11,Fhigh streets ` the beating heart of
OL,12,Four communities ` and that's what we
OL,13,Fwill do. What we're announcing today
OL,14,Fis just the start as we work to bring
OL,15,Fback hope across the country."
OL,17,FChancellor of the Exchequer John
OL,18,FHealey described pubs, clubs and live
OL,19,Fmusic venues as "the heart of
OL,20,Fcommunities across the UK".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784830712
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to cut business rates by
OL,4,C20% for pubs, clubs and music venues
OL,6,FHealey said: "We are determined to
OL,7,Fbring hope back, give businesses the
OL,8,Fsupport they need and generate growth
OL,9,Fin every postcode."
OL,11,FBurnham pledged to lead a "cost-of-
OL,12,Fliving government" during his first
OL,13,FCabinet meeting on Tuesday.
OL,15,FHis policies so far have included
OL,16,Fcutting VAT on energy bills, capping
OL,17,Fbus fares at #2, and now the reduction
OL,18,Fof business rates on pubs, clubs and
OL,19,Fmusic venues.
OL,26,@nD@NOUqD@SO]
