PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784830712
OL,3,CAndy Burnham to cut business rates by
OL,4,C20% for pubs, clubs and music venues
OL,6,FAccording to the Patriotic
OL,7,FMillionaires, a 2% tax on wealth over
OL,8,F#10 million could raise #24 billion a
OL,9,Fyear for the UK, while reforms to
OL,10,Fcapital gains tax could raise a
OL,11,Ffurther #12 billion.
OL,13,FPolling from the campaign group also
OL,14,Fshowed that 80% of UK millionaires
OL,15,Fsupport a 2% tax on wealth over #10
OL,16,Fmillion.
OL,18,F"As you decentralise political power,
OL,19,Fyou should also disperse economic
OL,20,Fpower," the open letter adds.
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
