OL,3,CAndy Burnham to cut business rates by
OL,4,C20% for pubs, clubs and music venues
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"Extreme wealth sitting idle in the
OL,12,Fhands of a few can be put to work:
OL,13,FReducing inequality, investing in
OL,14,Fsustainable jobs, strengthening
OL,15,Fhospitals, schools and social care,
OL,16,Fsupporting entrepreneurs with the
OL,17,Fskills and infrastructure they need,
OL,18,Fand giving small businesses access to
OL,19,Faffordable finance.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
