OL,3,CAndy Burnham to cut business rates by
OL,4,C20% for pubs, clubs and music venues
OL,6,F"Our wealth is our country's secret
OL,7,Fweapon ` let's get serious about using
OL,8,Fit."
OL,10,FLater on Thursday, Burnham will meet
OL,11,Fthe leaders of Scotland and Wales for
OL,12,Fthe first time since becoming Prime
OL,13,FMinister when he travels to Glasgow.
OL,15,FThe new PM backs further devolution,
OL,16,Fbut both First Minister of Scotland
OL,17,FJohn Swinney and the First Minister of
OL,18,FWales Rhun ap Iorwerth, want
OL,19,Findependence for their countries.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@DO]
